    <item>
      <title>美国核监管机构寻求“更高效”的反应堆审批</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/us-nuclear-regulator-pursues-more-efficient-reactor-approvals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高核监管机构的使命是简化新反应堆的审批并加速发电厂的建设。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/us-nuclear-regulator-pursues-more-efficient-reactor-approvals</guid>
